{
  "stem": "13219.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they used to tell us, from different-- like in Latvia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In, in, in the-- in Poland-- in Poland, which, which they already-- the Russians came in, and they let out all.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we-- they used to send them any place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Linz was a very, very big DP camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they had over 8,000 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a whole city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we met people from-- a matter of fact, a very good friend of my brother's was in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had the numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told us everything, what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we knew-- in the partisans, we knew some of it, what's going on already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end of the war-- yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The end of the German war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made us-- we were-- like I said before, I worked with a man who-- we, we had a truck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we used to go to Rovno to bring a lot of food for these Berezne.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while  we was in Rovno they said that the-- that we should all go to the square because Roosevelt died.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "April 12, 1945.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they made a very big to-do at that time, April 12, 1945.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then they made us-- one time when we were there, they made us go to a square because they caught German collaborators-- Ukraine and Polish people-- and they hang them on the big square.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made all the people should come down and see it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at the time I wasn't frightening anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nope.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't frightened anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was when we came from Russia to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, we were in the Galicia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a very anti-Semitic part of Poland-- Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they still didn't think that the Jews will be survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
